
Deploy Help

To use this deployment method for your server, first setup up the necessary file in config/deploy.php
	Start by entering in your application name as it exactly as it appears in GitHub
	Than enter in the repository url that you can get from GitHub
	Now setup all the ssh connections username, server, and location
	Now you good to go!
	The first push should always be passed with --initial at the end to setup all initial files and folders
Parameters:	--help, --initial, more coming soon...
	--help
		Read about all the variables and parameters you can pass into the deploy script for easy of use.
	--initial
		Passing the initial will allow the application to be posted while creating a directory for past releases and backups.
